Map #1

Park lights and open space in Cambridge, MA. This clean map clearly shows areas of open space in Cambridge and the concentration of park lights within those open spaces. The opacity of the open space reveals water underneath, so those are areas where park lights should not be expected. However, it does reveal the small set of open spaces that do not have park lights, leading to unpleasant or unsafe experiences.
